{"tid":2364333,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"無碼黃片（多圖附link)","createTime":"2021-01-13T02:12:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T06:27:30.000Z","uid":354728,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6ffd710a67c5571a9b62f132fe0408ccee383d94","tid":2364333,"uid":354728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T02:12:27.000Z","msg":"雖知廣東歌冇咩人聽，但呢首真係好想推介比更多人聽！<br />\n<br />\n陳健安On Chan - 惡夢經<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MjvnPgC0xgs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMjvnPgC0xgs&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvER%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=11495d5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MjvnPgC0xgs</a><br />\n<br />\n歌曲風格好有泰國indie band folk9/temp嘅feel 真心令到一個已經甚少聽廣東歌嘅人都會喜歡嘅歌<br />\n<br />\n同時嗰mv拍攝雖然feel到budget唔多，有啲鏡頭唔係拍得太靚，但係最重要係佢哋拍到個訊息出嚟。好有共嗚，香港人真係唔想再陷入個惡循環入面，所以睇完個MV加歌詞真係再係另一個層次。<br />\n<br />\n「繼續再睡再醒 惡夢美夢 永不停步」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rVheC6w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrVheC6w.png&h=0ba39e7c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8EEAnyc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8EEAnyc.png&h=62422426&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wLVvVTd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwLVvVTd.png&h=8a72a27b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YvROHye.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYvROHye.png&h=67f99efd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/480G2yf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F480G2yf.png&h=0afbfdf4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YS6Gh6B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYS6Gh6B.png&h=e5fa7460&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有一幕係三位主角喺士多入面偷偷食嘢，當比人發現嘅時候，即使好衝忙咁走都會擺返錢喺收銀檯上面。好似影射住其實香港人就係咁有規矩，即使係嘅惡劣嘅情況下都會保持最大嘅禮貌同規矩。<br />\n<br />\n呢首歌係廣東歌少有嘅風格，真係好想比更多人留意到佢嘅存在！一首咁正嘅歌竟然冇人講？！"},{"pid":"e